*** MySQLTuner-perl *** recommendation and optimization
-------------------------------------------------------
MySQLTuner is a script written in Perl that allows you to review a MySQL installation quickly and make adjustments to increase performance and stability. The current configuration variables and status data is retrieved and presented in a brief format along with some basic performance suggestions.
-------------------------------------------------------
***  Steps
---------
1. Download the file MySQLTuner .txt file.
2. Rename the .txt file to .pl
3. Make sure perl is installed on the server.
4. Then excute the below command as a root user.
# perl mysqltuner.pl
5. You will be listed with all the recommendation and optimization.

